        "text": ": here, as in ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "2 Timothy 4:20",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", the person bearing this name appears as an itinerant companion of St. Paul, and it therefore seems difficult to identify him with the Erastus of ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Romans 16:23",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", who is described as “treasurer” of the city, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "i.e.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", Corinth, since the tenure of such an office seems to presuppose a fixed residence. That the identification was not impossible is maintained by Wendt as against Meyer, but see “Erastus,” Hastings’ B.D. The name, as Meyer remarks, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Romans 16:23",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", was very common.—",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "greekheb",
        "text": "ἐπέσχε χρόνον",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ": verb, only used by Luke and Paul, and only here in this sense. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "greekheb",
        "text": "ἑαυτόν",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ": supplied after the verb; LXX, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Genesis 8:10",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
